ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v25.segment

Class RGS

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractSegment
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v25.segment.RGS
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Segment, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class RGS
extends AbstractSegment

    Represents an HL7 RGS message segment (Resource Group). This segment has the following fields:

    • RGS-1: Set ID - RGS (SI)
    • RGS-2: Segment Action Code (ID) optional
    • RGS-3: Resource Group ID (CE) optional
    See Also:
